title: Battle In The Bay, Week 5 Breakdown
description:
Welcome back to (debatable) with hosts Pablo Torre and Domonique Foxworth featuring Bill Barnwell! On today's show: What do you find most interesting about the ongoing situation between Draymond Green and Jordan Poole and what does it mean for the Warriors going forward? Plus, an NFL Week 5 breakdown where we debate whether teams such as the Packers, Rams, and Dolphins are cooked!
